      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 64.9 - 老子 64.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 64.8 - 老子 64.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九層之臺，起於累土；千里之行，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>the tower of nine storeys rose from a (small) heap of earth; the journey of a thousand li commenced with a single step.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
