      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 64.17 - 老子 64.18</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 64.14</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>民之從事，常於幾成而敗之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(But) people in their conduct of affairs are constantly ruining them when they are on the eve of success.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-064__align-013">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-064</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 64.19 - 老子 64.22</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 64.15 - 老子 64.16</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>慎終如始，則無敗事。是以聖人欲不欲，不貴難得之貨；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If they were careful at the end, as (they should be) at the beginning, they would not so ruin them. Therefore the sage desires what (other men) do not desire, and does not prize things difficult to get;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-064__align-014">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-064</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 64.23 - 老子 64.24</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 64.17</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>學不學，復眾人之所過。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>he learns what (other men) do not learn, and turns back to what the multitude of men have passed by.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
