      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 64.25 - 老子 64.26</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 64.18</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>以輔萬物之自然，而不敢為。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus he helps the natural development of all things, and does not dare to act (with an ulterior purpose of his own).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
